    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Agreements between a customer and supplier, by which the supplier will deliver goods or services on multiple delivery dates over a period of time, often negotiated to take advantage of predetermined pricing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
